reviews.text: Very busy, very big, outgoing staff, toilets could be a smidgen cleaner.... Place is like a maze I really like the old train out the front for people to take pictures of....

Good:One of the busiest station with DLR and over ground services!!

Bad: you need to wait long time to talk with someone or top uo Oyster card
Good place to catch a train only let down by no hot water in the loos.

Worst station, if you take the train from there,zone 2 to st pancras zone 1 they do not accept travel card, you have to pay as you go...i thought travel card covers the areas, but clearly not...most expensive public transport in the world for nothing...they still have to improve.
It's station where you can get trains from (haha), there is a coffe shop, europ car hire, W smith and toilets available. Few steps from westfield shopping centre.
